values: i keep forgetting about you journal. it's been soooo long.

I have only said this like a million times but Happy Birthday KT! I love you and I forget how to do the tags with a lj user name or I would have done that too. :) I am sappy about it, maybe because of the lack of sleep, but you mean the world to me.

fall is here.


maybe my mood will improve all quick like before it is winter and i hate that too.

it's been forever.


and i still got nothing to say.

another thunderstorm today. it makes me feel like i have to listen to the velvet underground. i feel sort of strange. i hope it doesn't mean a panic attack. it's prolly cause from tues morning until wed afternoon i worked 25 hrs. right back at work for another 7 this morning and 8 in the evening. weeeee. work work work. i just feel more out of sorts than normal. i need a moment to relax for real. i wish i had a really good plan for the weekend. i don't though. a good plan would be nice. i think i have to go to Chris's parents house cause it's his stepdad's bday. i'll be going cause it's Brennan's grandpa. otherwise, i would really like to have some me time. i'd like to get out of town but not sure where or with who. some place where some excitement happens. oh and where it'd be cheap, cause i am poor. even with all the working...

fucking a is it cold.


i have a free weekend and i am all about doing stuff...but it's freezing and snowing again.
brrrr. i don't think it's quite time to have the heat off.

i have been posting a lot more on myspace lately cause a lot more of my people's use it. life has been very, very rough. a lot is up with brennan and it's been hard on me. my life is an uphill struggle with a 200lb backpack. might as well mention that in this uphill struggle it is snowing and i am wearing converses. i might just be naked so that i can be embarrassed while i am at it. well,something like that. i laugh about it, talk openly and fake a smile. this is my life.

yellow bird flying
gets shot in the wing
good year for hunters
and christmas parties
and i hate
and i hate
and i hate
and i hate elevator music
the way we fight
the way i'm left here silent

oh these little earthquakes
here we go again
these little earthquakes
doesn't take much to
rip us into pieces

with vampires till dawn
we laughed in the faces of kings
never afraid to burn
and i hate

and i hate

watching us wither
black winged roses
that safely changed their COLOR

here we go again
these little earthquakes
doesn't take much to

can't reach you
give me life
give me pain
give me myself again

these little earthquakes
doesn't take much to
rip us into pieces

it's way to cold. i am glad i have lots of blankets to keep me warm. my bed sure is calling me. i have things i could write about but i have an awful headache. i had pt today and she was beating on my stupid knotted neck muscles and now i just ache. plus, i got a depo shot in the butt and for some odd reason that's all sore. i am also sore from some activites yesterday, good but sore. overall, i guess it's just been a sore day. hmmmm. dan gave me an early vd gift today. he got me the series "the lone gunmen", which i love and that just rocks. i think i may have made a squueeeee noise and then smiled entirely too big. i've been meaning to buy it. i can't wait to watch it again. anywho. headache, blah. more snow and cold tonight, blah. i am on my way to bed and my book. i can't keep my nose out of "his dark materials". i am almost done. i have loved it so far. i wish it wasn't so hard to hold my head up. :)
-19 sucks. aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah. i cannot feel my toes! i am hungry for food. however, i am FULL of coffee. very full of coffee.

i hate when brennan is home sick. it's like his meds don't work and then after going CRAZY all day, i get the plague too. i also had to miss going to KT's because brennan is just too much today. mia would not be driving me crazy. i always feel like an asshole when i don't go there. i take it seriously. stupid day. plus to top it off it's snowing again. it's all white and blur outside. i hate winter. bitch moan, bitch moan.
i feel about as blah as blah gets.

i have a headache. i hate nights where brennan has a rough bedtime. i called chris so that he could talk to him before i yelled some more (i hate, HATE yelling and it makes me very sad to do it, i wanna cry afterwards.)and chris was like he's prolly upset cause he doesn't want us to live apart anymore. well bullshit. cause then he followed by saying brennan didn't sleep well last night. it was totally a case of brennan was overtired and not cooperating because of it. also i was getting angry, which i know doesn't help but i am only human myself. chris and i seem to fight almost as much apart as together. the last few days have been good but still. he gets angry over little things or doesn't listen to me (like always) and then says i am one-sided, when in reality it is often him. he tends to be only out for himself. he needs to change that. i sacrifice things all the time. often times my sanity. or my well being or whatever else i can give give give. i dunno. bad bedtime puts me in a bad mood and then makes me feel like a rotten mommy for not being able to handle it. it makes me not want brennan and then i get really angry because i love him very much. he is my world. it's just sometimes and more so lately i don't know what to do. i just don't want to feel so robotic and worthless, stagnant or like a bad mommy. sometimes everything boils into one thing. ack. i have a headache. i don't even know if i make sense.

i am so angry i could spit today. i would love to go into bigger details but then i get angrier. we'll just put it as chris thinks that if he goes to his friends houses with brennan that i don't need to know the phone numbers or addresses of where they are. i say i have a right to know if he's staying overnight some place with him or gonna be there for hours with him either shutting his phone off, which is what i suspect, or "the batteries dying" every time he goes some place. last night i got angry and i left him messages. 4 messages that got angrier when he shut off his phone. he said i was psycho because i said if we can't work this out, i'm gonna involve my case worker or call the police next time. i think i have every right to know where brennan is...i don't need to know that they went to walmart but if he is gonna be gone for hours or overnights, then i do. a simple call and a way to get ahold of them is all i need. i am very worried sometimes when he takes brennan. chris's car is not the best. i don't trust all his friends around my son and i can't do much about that but i do feel uncomfortable. i am allowed to feel uncomfortable. i don't care if chris wants to start seeing someone or whatever. that has nothing to do with this. brennan is my life right now and if i call and am ignored, i am going to be mad. and one simple call could change that.

i've stopped saying things here. now all i do is blog on myspace. i miss when livejournal was more fun. i miss a lot of things. boo hoo. i am not excited for the holidays. i do hope that you all have great ones though. filled with lots of whatever it is you want.
this song always make me laugh until i cry. cause me and god are watching scotty die. woohoo. it's official, i caught thirty today. this evening should be full of something. i hope it's fun. :)

I am Stuck on Littledirtyliar, 'Cause Littledirtyliar's Stuck on Me.

i got a fortune cookie tonight and it said " do not let others take advantage of you". now wouldn't it be nice if that were true?

it's that time of year again where i begin a few days early and complain about getting older. i will shortly be thirty or if you ask me, 25 again. i am not excited for thirty. i don't wanna grow up anymore.

i went to court today for my fireworks ticket. i got out of the ticket but had to pay 25 dollars for the court fee. i barely have that. the judge was funny though. he said even though oktoberfest is sorta like a week long 4th of july party, i prolly should save the fireworks for then. on my way out, i found that i had an 8 dollar parking ticket. sometimes, oh wait, i never get a damn break, i swear. i am surprised the judge let the ticket go. he wasn't going to but then he did. maybe that was my own second of luck.

feelings. i hate having feelings. although i would say in the last few days my mood has been better. getting better. i think it's prolly the zoloft but that's okay. maybe i am getting my life on track? maybe it's cause i'm not taking shit from anyone? maybe it's cause i'm tired? who knows. life just keeps on going anyways. maybe some day i will have it figured out.

give me your vertical
your horizontal line
i want to take each of them
bend them to fit mine
the world is too good for me
i am such a naughty girl
but when we're together
we're too good for this world

not even cat macros are making me feel better. so far the move has not really made me any happier. just stressed in a new way and missing my baby when he goes to chris's house, formerly known as my house. i miss my house damnit. like being able to do laundry or dishes without doing them wrong. or take a shower or give brennan a bath without doing it wrong. i know something else will have to be wrong. here i am on eggshells agin. today sucked too cause i am waiting for food stamp help and that got fucked up my boss shorted me 13 hrs on my paycheck and weeee....i have bills due in 4 days. what am i gonna do? i may have to call my mom and i hate that. hate it. she is gonna guilt me and i cant take that either. most days now i sit with no internet, no radio, no nothing just reading, talking to no one and falling asleep cause i have to be quiet so dan can sleep. he says i dont have to but i know i should be. i really hate my life. i would love a do over please.
well today really really sucks. i so wanted to have a good halloween.

why do i suck at life? seriously?

i move in two weeks. i cannot believe it. i am getting very excited, even though some things about moving make me sad. i still wanna talk to chris in a civil way and all. i hope it can be like that. hmmmm. i cannot think of things to say whenever i get to my journal. oh, how i miss being able to say the things i need to say. the things i need to get off my chest. i try and they won't come. too much time worrying about others feelings. tonight i am a bit sad but better than yesterday. after brennan goes to be that may change. i dont know. i get lonely. i may have said this before but i hate hate hate being alone. alone and i are not friends. at all. ewww. anyways. brennan wants me to watch invader zim and so off i shall go.
my life is so busy right now. i don't even know where to start.

still alive?

2. I've come to realize that, I talk :
more when i am drunk.

my boo boo so much it hurts.

lots of crap i don't care about.

myself and a few other things along the way.

people bug me.
 
I've come to realize that there is no number 7.

annoying. very, very annoying.

i want tacos too!

10. I've come to realize that, I'll always be :
crazy and i do not care.

11. I've come to realize that, I have a crush on :
i have no crush.

12. I've come to realize that, The last time I cried was :
about 45 minutes ago.

is a piece of shit that better ring here in a few...

i should prolly stay in bed.

i should prolly take sleeping pills.

making things better.

was not a good day.

20. I've come to realize that, Tonight I will :
need to make it a better day.

21. I've come to realize that, Tomorrow I will :
try and try again.

22. I've come to realize that, I really want to:
figure out my life and that this was not as fun as i wanted it to be.

23. I've come to realize that, The person who is most likely to do this:
umm. no one. people still use lj?

i'm up and down with feelings but i know i am doing the right thing. strange how the right thing has to sometimes feel that way. i think i may half way die of shocking life style changes. if i find myself happy and happy for more than moments, it may be just a lot to handle. i am glad for some friends. some who put up with me and do it time and time again. i may need you all soon. i'm moving out the first weekend in november. now i need to change myself from saying "if i move out" to "when i move out". and i need to make that stick.

i can't stop thinking. i hate that it hurts.

It is Miss KT's birthday today. i forget how to do the tags for the user names (she's eating_dust) and i am to just woke up from sleep to look and fix it but anyways HAPPY BIRTHDAY DOLL! i love you bunches and bunches. i hope to day and future days are wonderful. :) or at least coffee or rum filled with some sunshine and a smile.

i love mia moo. i am glad she is such a great little girl to babysit for. it makes this day, that i already don't like toooo much, better. i think i just need sleep. and the answer to all my problems. wouldn't that be great? hmmm. at least brennan is doing well in school. every time i check, it's good (or i hear nothing, which means good). i am sure he will have a bad day or three at some point but so far *knocks on wood* so good. that makes things for me a little better. i feel relief there. sigh. i can't wait to go home and sleep. i also wanna go to target for halloween shopping and i wanna buy shoes cause that makes me feel happy. hurm. so much to do.
with no help from me, brennan just told chris he was tool and right after that he told me that jiji was digging in the garbage because he just wanted "the goods." :)
chris and i have decided on a separation. now to work out details.

i want to live, to feel a face
that isn't there
i want to live
i roll over and you're not there
i'm only standing on the shore

i had some friends but i want more...

i see the future and it's all mine
want to be perfect, i'm taking my time
i'll try not to act like i'm so far away
i try to be right in whatever i say
deeper feelings recur again & again & again & again
a complex spiral leads me to spin...


i want to live
to see the earth turn one more time
i wanna live
to feel a hand that isn't mine
i'm only standing on the shore
i had some fun but i want more
i'll try not to act like i'm so far away
i try to be right in whatever i say
deeper feelings recur again & again & again & again
a complex spiral leads me to spin...

it rained and rained all day yesterday. we got well over 7 and 1/2 inches. we are expected to get more today. people near winona drowned in their cars. we had at least 9 cars stall out on our street. one car died completely and with one car, the people couldn't get out of for awhile. i called for help but before the police could get here or ever show up for that matter, someone with a pickup truck helped them to safety. the water was up on my car doors. the waves lapped our front steps like the wave pool at noah's ark. my neighbors front lawn was a lake. we don't even live by the river. no one can get to my job because they all live in minnesota. it is a mess around here.

i am actually enjoying todays cold and rainy weather. i love when it is about this temp outside. 65-75 is fine with me. i cant wait for fall and i know it will go by fast. way to fast and then stupid winter. i had a really great day yesterday with dan and brennan. we went fishing in lansing and didnt catch anything. mostly we got sucked under the rocks. it was not as good as the fishing the three of us did last weekend at my parents house. there we caught a ton of fish and had a great dinner of beer batter fried fish. mmmm. anyway. after fishing we went to a park in waukon where brennan knocked me off a teeter totter (never had to spell that before) type thing...hard to describe and really smashed up my right arm/elbow. ive got a few decent purple bruises and it hurts. plus it hit my right shoulder which is part of the neck and shoulder issues that i have been having go on. it was a park i played in has a kid and something that was there since i was little. also the rocket was still there. it was fun. later in the afternoon while walking at twin springs in decorah my shoulder popped out of place very loudly. it hurt so bad i got dizzy for a second. its still pretty sore and strange feeling today. i guess im not really sure if it went in or out of place. my shoulder is so messed up anyways. oh well. the walk was beautiful. it felt like fall outside and we saw tons and tons of cool mushrooms of all kinds. some were bright red and some were bright yellow and orange. it was just a perfect day. i need more of those.

good morning dear, i think i'm losing it
can't find my way and i'm, i'm getting used to it
sun refused to shine on this side of the street
i'm not recognizing anyone i meet
trying to hide in the shadow of the sun
you're not fooling anyone...
i just got back from the doctor. i got 2 muscle relaxant injections. one in each shoulder muscle. woohoo. we have never done this before so we shall see how i feel later. hopefully fine.

headache headache go away come again another day. i really wanna post about my trip and some of the pics. i just have had such a problem with my neck since i got back. it gives me the worst fucking headaches. i see the dr tomorrow though so that should be good.

im back. i was in montana yesterday morning. in the last 2 days i drove at least 20 hrs. i finally got a shower tonight. i so should be in bed. and am going there reaaal soon. just wanted to say i had a really good time. i think dan did too. i need to post pictures some time. maybe after i sleep for a day.
i leave tomorrow and will be back august 6th. woohoo. :) i already miss brennan so much it hurts. i love my baby boo.

due to working a bunch this weekend, getting the book late saturday afternoon, dan's birthday (it's actually today, HAPPY BIRTHDAY!!!!!) and needing to sleep a bit inbetween, it took me until just now to finish the book. now we can discuss and i will begin again to answer jon's phone calls and look at the internet.
